cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and natural language processing. The use of a multi-layer neural network for phrase projection suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The optimization of end-to-end machine translation results could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of semantic representations and the evaluation of translation performance could suggest a connection to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
